{
  "id": "adv_event_2602_01_04",
  "title": "しなやかな強さ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、すずにゃん、なんでついて来たの？\nただジュース買いに行くだけだから大丈夫だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.6333106041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.6666432381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、お祝いだし、ドーナツも買いに行こうかな？\nコンビニまで行って、お砂糖ふりふりするやつを――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6666432381,
      "endTime": 16.5219493866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.5886148453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣\n無理、しなくていいんですのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5886148453,
      "endTime": 21.6734449387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.8886148453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……なんのことかな……無理なんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8886148453,
      "endTime": 28.3405647278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5405645371
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は頑張りましたわ\nその努力、私は見ていましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5405645371,
      "endTime": 35.053899574300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.4405632656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "すず、ちゃん……っ……ぐすっ、うっ、うっ……\nうわぁぁぁんっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4405632656,
      "endTime": 46.9980238599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1980236691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんがセンターになって……嬉しいよ\nすっごく嬉しい、けど……心がぎゅってなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1980236691,
      "endTime": 59.7980238599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.0000025431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ううううっ、悔しい、悔しいよぉ……\n芽衣も……芽衣もセンターになりたかった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3980290096,
      "endTime": 71.5324959438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7324957531
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわよね\n芽衣だって、月ストの一員ですものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7324957531,
      "endTime": 78.4924957913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6991624197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "一員じゃないよ、芽衣は、芽衣は中心になりたかった\nすずちゃんみたいに、みんなの中心になりたかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6991624197,
      "endTime": 91.0371157966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.2556781359
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.1871171317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "「四人それぞれが嵐になろう」って言ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2371171317,
      "endTime": 97.493851789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.6938515983
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、ここまですずちゃんが中心に\nいてくれたからこそ、月ストは頑張れたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6938515983,
      "endTime": 106.6691808067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7858477913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "中心って……私みたいに、って……\nもしかして、芽衣がセンターになりたかったのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8358477913,
      "endTime": 119.9238526665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1358477913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "あの時のすずちゃんみたいに、芽衣も支えたかったの\nすずちゃん達が忙しいなら、芽衣が力になりたかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1358477913,
      "endTime": 131.3683648431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、あの頃からずっと、すずちゃんに憧れてるんだよ\nすずちゃんは大切な友達で、芽衣の憧れなんだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3666666667,
      "endTime": 146.0314353309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.5683646523
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.2314351402
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "っ……芽衣……もう、そういうことはもっと早く言って\nくださいまし。そこまで思ってくれているなら、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2314351402,
      "endTime": 159.2333251952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.4647633872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "私、次こそは、琴乃にも渚にも負けず、センターに\n立ってみせます。芽衣に、恥ずかしくないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4647633872,
      "endTime": 170.57616952269998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.7647633872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "うん……うん？　えぇ！？　なんでそうなるの！？\nすずにゃんがセンターだと芽衣がセンターになれないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7647633872,
      "endTime": 179.4709542594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.6709540687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "細かいことを言いますわねぇ。じゃあ、負けないくらい\n頑張りなさい。もちろん、私も頑張りますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.6709540687,
      "endTime": 189.2207957587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.4042874021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん……。うん、次は絶対に負けないからね！\n芽衣がセンターに立って、すずにゃんに見せてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.4042874021,
      "endTime": 199.8832892104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.0832890196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんみたいにかっこ良くて\n麻奈ちゃんみたいにみんなを幸せにする、芽衣の姿を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.0832890196,
      "endTime": 206.3897744818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.5897742911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "その意気ですわ。と言いたいところですが、麻奈様？\n好きなのは知っていましたが……なぜ麻奈様ですの？",
