      "text": "ま、待って待って！\nいつの間にこんな凄いものを作ってくれたの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.2261254315,
      "endTime": 253.4012934689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "資料集めは、企画の話を聞いた時からですが\n渚ちゃん用に調整したのは今さっきですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.5679650312,
      "endTime": 260.882114697,
      "sfxList": [
