      "text": "センター以外にも、力になれることはありますから\nといっても、次のセンターには、なる気でいますけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.0887580877,
      "endTime": 276.8687576299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗にも約束しましたし、渚ちゃんからも、沢山\n学ばせてもらいます。私、アイドルが大好きですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.0687574392,
      "endTime": 286.5333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、強力なライバルだ～……\nありがとう、沙季ちゃん。頼りにしてるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.8091098791,
      "endTime": 295.5491094595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "はいはーい！　次は芽衣の番だよー！\nMCとライブの衣装を考えてきたんだー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.7491092688,
