      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインっていうのが一目で分かるような配色や\nデザインになっているわね。いい方向性だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.1556026148,
      "endTime": 326.2556028056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、さすがは私が嫉妬したほどのセンスですわ\n『shiny shiny』の時を思い出しますわねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.4556026148,
      "endTime": 335.7110671686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って！？\nなんだか二人とも、センターの私より頑張ってない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.8556005802,
      "endTime": 341.41197255509996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "当然です\n私達も、月ストを引っ張っていくと決めていますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.6119723644,
      "endTime": 347.20507892039996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん！\nそれに芽衣は、月ストの次期センターだからね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.4050787296,
      "endTime": 353.422629961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "さらっと私の自己紹介を奪わないでくださいまし！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.6226297703,
      "endTime": 358.3798860874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな、頼もしいな。本気でぶつかりあって）\n（想いを交わせるのは、ライブバトルだけじゃないんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358.589296437,
      "endTime": 368.58058919980004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "（全ての経験が、私達を強くしてくれる）\n（そばに一番の光があるから、月はもっと輝けるんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 368.7805890091,
      "endTime": 380.54866190030003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2602_01_04-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、じゃあ私も負けないよ。ライブに向けて\n何か考えてみるよ。バレンタインらしい、とびきりのを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 380.7486617096,
      "endTime": 391.2209973344,
      "sfxList": []
